  "Description": {
    "English": "The building block of all organic life. Of critical importance to space travelers, as Carbon is used to <span class=\"name name-fuel\">recharge mining equipment</span>.<br> <br>The <span class=\"name name-technology\">Mining Laser</span> will harvest Carbon from trees, plants, and all other forms of vegetable.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "所有有机生命的基石。对空间旅行者至关重要，因为碳可用于<span class=\"name name-fuel\">为开采设备充能</span>。<br> <br><span class=\"name name-technology\">开采激光</span>将从树木、植物和所有其他形式的植被中获取碳。",
    "TencentChinese": "所有有机生命的基石。对空间旅行者至关重要，因为碳可用于<span class=\"name name-fuel\">为开采设备充能</span>。<br> <br><span class=\"name name-technology\">开采激光</span>将从树木、植物和所有其他形式的植被中获取碳。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "所有有機生命的基礎。對太空旅行者特別重要，因為碳能用來<span class=\"name name-fuel\">補充採礦配備的能量</span>。<br> <br><span class=\"name name-technology\">採礦雷射</span>能從樹木、植物以及任何形式的植披中收集碳。"
  },
